(1) Upon consideration of the application the District Secretary if satisfied as to the bona fides of the club shall, subject to the provisions of subsection (3), in his discretion grant the same and shall issue a Certificate of Registration in Form 2 in the Schedule and thereupon the club shall be deemed to be duly registered.
