(4) An appeal against the refusal of the District Secretary to grant any application under this section shall lie to the High Court which may reverse such decision where it is satisfied that the District Secretary ought to have granted the application. [As amended by No. 7 of 1963 and, Nos. 27 and 33 of 1966, and Act No. 13 of 1994 ]
